who killed his mother.

28:17.734 --> 28:19.703
Admiral Whiskers?

28:19.737 --> 28:23.673
I love that guy.

28:26.144 --> 28:29.079
This is a splendid start.
Who else?

28:29.113 --> 28:30.681
Hmm. You know what?

28:30.714 --> 28:33.750
Let's start small. A trinity.

28:33.784 --> 28:36.386
Hmm. Hmm, I like it.

28:36.420 --> 28:38.490
I like it. A menage-a-us.

28:38.522 --> 28:42.660
