31:50.248 --> 31:52.048
I'll get her, Jane.

31:52.083 --> 31:53.931
Don't worry.

31:55.586 --> 31:56.354
Kay...

31:56.354 --> 31:57.521
Come here, monkey.

31:57.521 --> 32:00.724
<i>Sweet, sweet baby...
Baby...</i>

32:00.759 --> 32:03.727
I know you think
this is how it has to be,

32:03.727 --> 32:06.096
but this isn't healing, Jane.

32:06.130 --> 32:11.130
Forgetting and hiding
isn't healing.

32:11.935 --> 32:16.306
You have to go up.

32:16.306 --> 32:20.111
I can't.

32:20.144 --> 32:22.980
We're safer here.

32:23.013 --> 32:25.950
We're happy, aren't we?

