34:31.876 --> 34:36.146
- So, rescue Danny.
- I can't.

34:36.179 --> 34:38.730
I need your help.

34:50.293 --> 34:54.797
A long time ago,
I had a daughter.

34:54.833 --> 34:58.936
She's extraordinary
and everything to me,

34:58.969 --> 35:02.072
and I'm afraid...

35:02.106 --> 35:06.456
she is a danger to all of us.

35:07.644 --> 35:11.614
All I ever wanted was to live
one day longer than she did,

35:11.648 --> 35:13.884
to protect her.

35:13.918 --> 35:17.621
To protect others.

35:17.655 --> 35:22.655
That's why I created
each one of you.

35:27.164 --> 35:32.164
I need to study any means possible
of extending my own life.

35:34.371 --> 35:39.110
So, we were lab rats.
Just like Mr. Nobody said.

35:39.143 --> 35:43.014
Yes, at first.
I can't deny that.

35:43.047 --> 35:47.684
Okay, I'm sorry,
but invoking your daughter now,

35:47.717 --> 35:49.085
it's fucking evil.

35:49.119 --> 35:50.288
It's the truth.

35:50.320 --> 35:52.590
I hid her for years on Danny,

35:52.623 --> 35:57.623
who graciously accepted
to be her caretaker.

35:57.699 --> 35:59.862
Somehow,

35:59.896 --> 36:02.432
Mr. Nobody

36:02.432 --> 36:04.335
has found out about her,

36:04.367 --> 36:09.367
and he's trapped them both
inside this painting.

36:11.007 --> 36:15.079
Please.

36:15.112 --> 36:18.349
She's all I've got left.

36:18.382 --> 36:21.686
Tell you what. I'll help you
with your daughter

36:21.719 --> 36:25.289
