invent a time machine

36:25.322 --> 36:29.360
that gets me back the 30 years
I lost with mine.

36:29.393 --> 36:34.099
Till then, fuck you forever!

36:34.132 --> 36:37.501
And Danny? You're just gonna
turn your back on them?

36:37.501 --> 36:39.003
Even though
they had no part in this?

36:39.003 --> 36:43.039
I'm sorry, what part of "fuck
you forever" was in Hebrew?

36:43.074 --> 36:45.577
I'll do it.

36:45.610 --> 36:48.246
For Danny.
Even your daughter.

36:50.014 --> 36:52.182
Not for you.

36:52.215 --> 36:54.585
Wait!
You're doing this?

36:54.619 --> 36:57.320
Niles Caulder, you're an awful,

36:57.355 --> 37:01.760
vermin-infested,
garbage... person.

37:01.793 --> 37:05.329
But so help me, I'm going
into that painting too.

37:05.362 --> 37:07.664
I was terrible
as a human being,

37:07.699 --> 37:12.070
and even worse
as an acting teacher.

37:12.103 --> 37:16.440
The only time I don't feel
like a complete asshole

37:16.474 --> 37:19.811
is when I'm dealing with...

37:19.844 --> 37:23.614
whatever you would
call this foolishness.

37:23.646 --> 37:25.248
Larry.

37:25.282 --> 37:27.751
Does my opinion
even matter?

37:27.751 --> 37:28.954
Cliff.

37:28.987 --> 37:31.922
Great! Now I'm the fucking
asshole who's a fucking asshole

37:31.922 --> 37:33.625
if I don't walk
into the fucking painting.

37:33.625 --> 37:35.900
Of course I'm gonna fucking
walk into the fucking painting,

37:35.900 --> 37:36.925
because, let's be honest,

37:36.925 --> 37:40.164
who the fuck else is enough of a fucking
asshole to walk into a fucking painting?

37:40.164 --> 37:42.599
Let's go!

37:42.634 --> 37:46.704
Okay, so get into
the painting... somehow,

37:46.737 --> 37:49.172
and then rescue Danny
and your daughter somehow.

37:49.206 --> 37:50.842
Getting in is gonna be
the easy part.

37:50.875 --> 37:52.844
It's the getting out
that's gonna be tricky.

37:52.876 --> 37:54.746
Why?
What do we have to do?

37:54.778 --> 37:57.780
I don't know. That's why
it's gonna be tricky.

37:57.815 --> 38:00.585
Ah. Okay.

38:02.052 --> 38:04.489
So, what do we do?
Just stare at this thing?

38:04.521 --> 38:06.891
Keep staring. Keep staring.

38:14.565 --> 38:16.300
Where is everyone?

38:18.436 --> 38:22.005
Danny, you okay?
What's going...

38:22.039 --> 38:25.789
Uh, can't see. All right.

38:31.248 --> 38:33.050
Danny, what about her?

38:33.083 --> 38:34.485
She safe?

38:36.521 --> 38:38.170
Uh... Guys?

38:47.297 --> 38:51.402
What the hell is that?

38:51.434 --> 38:54.204
Now comes
your reckoning!

38:54.237 --> 38:55.606
Oh, God.

38:55.639 --> 38:59.076
Behold!
I am His right hand.

38:59.108 --> 39:02.313
His scythe! Use me, Father!

39:02.346 --> 39:07.217
I am your disciple,
your fifth horseman!

39:07.251 --> 39:08.550
Take cover!

39:11.688 --> 39:14.190
Shit! Shit!

39:14.224 --> 39:15.458
Shit!

39:15.492 --> 39:20.492
Shit! Shit, shit, shit,
shit, shit, shit, shit!

39:20.898 --> 39:24.235
<i>♪ Oh, Danny boy ♪</i>

39:24.268 --> 39:26.269
<i>♪ Danny boy ♪</i>

39:26.302 --> 39:28.405
I'm so sorry, Danny boy!

39:28.438 --> 39:30.708
Oh, my God.
Danny was right. You came.

39:30.742 --> 39:32.677
I'm so happy to see you guys.

39:32.677 --> 39:34.244
Man, what the hell are you doing?

39:35.780 --> 39:38.648
I fucked up. I fucked up.

39:38.682 --> 39:42.119
I fucked up so hard.

39:42.152 --> 39:44.554
I was happy here, you know.

39:44.588 --> 39:47.759
This guy shows up,
Mr. Nobody, offering me

39:47.791 --> 39:52.128
bags of Lincoln,
da Vinci, ZZ Top.

39:52.161 --> 39:55.666
Their beards tasted so good.

39:55.699 --> 39:59.336
And I told him...

39:59.369 --> 40:01.505
I told him everything.

40:01.539 --> 40:06.344
You sold her out.

40:15.353 --> 40:16.952
What did you do?

40:16.952 --> 40:18.389
What did I do?

40:18.422 --> 40:21.960
I mean, sure, I trapped Danny
in this goddamn painting

40:21.992 --> 40:25.963
before realizing that
it would turn me into this...

40:25.963 --> 40:27.197
this husk!

40:27.231 --> 40:29.733
All I wanted to do

40:29.766 --> 40:32.036
was to meet that Cro-Magnon
squeeze of yours,

40:32.070 --> 40:34.271
and lo and behold,
all that remains

40:34.306 --> 40:37.809
is an adorable, almighty
chip off the old block.

40:37.842 --> 40:40.478
If you so much as harmed
a hair on her head...

40:43.215 --> 40:48.052
She enlarged those two
backstabbing vermin!

40:48.085 --> 40:50.989
Have you ever tried
talking sense to a pest

40:51.021 --> 40:55.226
while he enjoys his very own
re-enactment of a Kaiju movie?

40:55.226 --> 40:56.360
It is impossible!

40:56.393 --> 40:58.396
Shut up!
Look, we need a plan.

40:58.429 --> 41:00.931
Look, we were the only people
in this whole entire world

41:00.965 --> 41:03.235
who got Danny's SOS
and followed it here.

41:03.268 --> 41:05.936
We're standing inside the heart
of a sentient street,

41:05.969 --> 41:08.672
inside a magic painting
with a giant-ass cockroach,

41:08.706 --> 41:09.907
a guy who hunts beards, and...

41:09.940 --> 41:12.175
And an inter-dimensional
fuck-up.

41:14.012 --> 41:16.047
If anybody's gonna save Danny

41:16.081 --> 41:19.483
and the Chief's daughter,
it's gonna be us.

41:19.516 --> 41:22.967
Fine. What's this plan?

41:27.458 --> 41:30.295
This way. Quickly!

41:30.327 --> 41:35.266
She's in the Doll Hospital,
down the stairs.

41:35.298 --> 41:36.900
That wasn't so bad.

41:36.934 --> 41:39.804
Maybe the giant roach
found a giant turd to chow down on

41:39.836 --> 41:43.074
and forgot all about us.

41:47.744 --> 41:49.713
It's the roach, isn't it?

41:59.155 --> 42:02.159
Oh, fuck my life!

42:02.192 --> 42:06.297
Jane, run!

42:06.329 --> 42:07.664
The fuck!

42:16.840 --> 42:20.811
Come and get it, asshole!

42:20.844 --> 42:23.695
Oh, shit. Oh, shit!

42:27.784 --> 42:30.353
No. Find my daughter.

42:30.387 --> 42:33.686
The Doll Hospital. Go.

42:49.507 --> 42:53.409
I was supposed
to be the villain

42:53.443 --> 42:57.648
of this shitty piece.

42:57.681 --> 43:00.784
I was bested by a little girl,

43:00.818 --> 43:04.454
and thrown out of my own
criminal organization

43:04.487 --> 43:08.492
by a rat and a roach.

43:08.525 --> 43:11.327
Me...

43:11.362 --> 43:14.032
The big bad. The black hat.

43:14.065 --> 43:17.835
You can't make this shit up!

43:17.869 --> 43:22.472
Yesterday, a 13-year-old girl told me
to fuck my face with a weed-whacker.

43:24.407 --> 43:27.378
Congratulations.

43:27.411 --> 43:29.480
We both suck.

43:29.512 --> 43:31.181
That's one way
to tell the story.

43:31.215 --> 43:32.516
It's the truth.

43:32.550 --> 43:34.885
It's the past.

43:34.918 --> 43:38.521
The future is still yours
for the making.

43:38.556 --> 43:41.592
Why? What's the point?

43:41.626 --> 43:45.329
I know what it's like
to be a nobody.

43:45.362 --> 43:49.134
But as bad as that felt,
I'd rather be nobody than nothing.

43:49.166 --> 43:51.369
And that is exactly
what you're going to be

43:51.402 --> 43:54.472
if you don't quit
